2006-02-22    obenke

	* plugin/cimplugXen.c, plugin/metricXen.c, plugin/metricXen.readme,
	plugin/repositoryXen.c, provider/mof/Linux_XenMetric.mof,
	provider/mof/Linux_XenMetric.registration:
	Bug 1436671: New plugin for Xen (virtualization project) metrics.
	The following metrics are implemented:
	- TotalCPUTime
	- ActiveVirtualProcessors
	- ExternalViewTotalCPUPercentage
	- PartitionClaimedMemory
	- PartitionClaimedMaximumMemory
	- HostFreePhysicalMemory
	- ClaimedMemoryPercentage
	- HostMemoryPercentage

2006-02-22    <mihajlov@localhost.localdomain>

	* mreposl.c, util/reposcfg.c, reposd.conf: 
	Bug 1436591: Added new config option "ExpirationInterval" allowing
	to modify the local repository history length.

	* gatherc.h, repos.h, repos.c, rrepos.h, rrepos.c, 
	reposd.c, reposctl.c: 
	Bug 1436488: Added a new filtered get operation allowing
	to limit the number of returned metric values.
	Further, added support for a global filter applying to
	regular get operations if set.

	* marshal.h, marshal.c:
	Bug 1436488: Added new functions marshal_fix, unmarshal_fix
	in support of the get/set global filter calls.

	* provider/OSBase_MetricRepositoryServiceProvider.c,
	provider/mof/Linux_Metricmof:
	Bug 1436488: Extended class definition of MetricRepositoryService
	to include enumeration limit properties and a method to set
	the enumeration limits.
	
